<br />lot more in relation to each other.</p>
        <p begin="00:22:52.830" end="00:22:54.850" tts:direction="ltr">That's number 18.</p>
        <p begin="00:22:54.850" end="00:22:58.330" tts:direction="ltr">You have now completed 18 different ways</p>
        <p begin="00:22:58.330" end="00:23:00.230" tts:direction="ltr">to visualize a bar chart and it's been</p>
        <p begin="00:23:00.230" end="00:23:07.030" tts:direction="ltr">a wonderful journey doing this bar chart
<br />bonanza with you. Happy visit.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
